ctpp2 (2.8.3-4) unstable; urgency=low

  [ Vasudev Kamath ]
  * Fix libctpp2-2.symbols file by replacing architecture dependent
    symbols with demangled symbols tagged as (c++).
    Closes: bug#705135.
  * debian/rules:
    + Passed -v$(DEB_UPSTREAM_VERSION) to dpkg-gensymbols to avoid it
      from taking debian versions while creating symbol file.
  * 1004_ftbfs_fix_kfreebsd-hurd.patch is introduced to skip iconv library
    detection on Hurd and GNU/kFreeBSD system.
    Closes: bug#705134      

  [ Jonas Smedegaard ]
  * Add README.source emphasizing control.in file as *not* a
    show-stopper for contributions, referring to wiki page for details.

 -- Vasudev Kamath <kamathvasudev@gmail.com>  Sun, 21 Apr 2013 17:42:37 +0530

